  "title": "Counter",
  "description": "<p>Near Hougang <strong>T</strong>CM wellness Clinic is looking for a Full-Time Counter staff.<br /><br />The role involves customer reception, appointment scheduling, payment handling, and basic administrative duties. <br /><br />Candidates should have basic computer skills and be familiar with Excel and Word, possess good communication skills, and maintain a positive customer service attitude. Knowledge of social media platforms such as Facebook, Instagram, or TikTok will be an advantage. <br /><br />The position requires working 5–6 days per week, including weekends and public holidays on a rotational basis.<br /><br />We offer a basic salary of $2000 with experience + commission, a stable working environment, friendly team culture, and opportunities for salary increment and career growth. <br /><br />Fresh graduates are welcome, and training will be provided.</p><p>Interested candidates are welcome to WhatsApp: 91055788</p>",
